Hal ata ‘ala al-insani heenun mina alddahri lam yakun shay-an mathkooran
Inna khalaqna al-insana min nutfatin amshajin nabtaleehi faja’alnahu samee’an baseeran
Inna hadaynahu alssabeela imma shakiran wa-imma kafooran
Inna a’tadna lilkafireena salasila waaghlalan wasa’eeran
Inna al-abrara yashraboona min ka/sin kana mizajuha kafooran
‘aynan yashrabu biha ‘ibadu Allahi yufajjiroonaha tafjeeran
Yoofoona bialnnathri wayakhafoona yawman kana sharruhu mustateeran
Wayut’imona altta’ama ‘ala hubbihi miskeenan wayateeman waaseeran
Innama nut’imukum liwajhi Allahi la nureedu minkum jazaan wala shukooran
Inna nakhafu min rabbina yawman ‘aboosan qamtareeran
Fawaqahumu Allahu sharra thalika alyawmi walaqqahum nadratan wasurooran
Wajazahum bima sabaroo jannatan wahareeran
Muttaki-eena feeha ‘ala al-ara-iki la yarawna feeha shamsan wala zamhareeran
Wadaniyatan ‘alayhim thilaluha wathullilat qutoofuha tathleelan
Wayutafu ‘alayhim bi-aniyatin min fiddatin waakwabin kanat qawareera
Qawareera min fiddatin qaddarooha taqdeeran
Wayusqawna feeha ka/san kana mizajuha zanjabeelan
‘aynan feeha tusamma salsabeelan
Wayatoofu ‘alayhim wildanun mukhalladoona itha raaytahum hasibtahum lu/lu- an manthooran
Wa-itha raayta thamma raayta na’eeman wamulkan kabeeran
‘aliyahum thiyabu sundusin khudrun wa-istabraqun wahulloo asawira min fiddatin wasaqahum rabbuhum sharaban tahooran
Inna hatha kana lakum jazaan wakana sa’yukum mashkooran
Inna nahnu nazzalna ‘alayka alqur-ana tanzeelan
Faisbir lihukmi rabbika wala tuti’ minhum athiman aw kafooran
Waothkuri isma rabbika bukratan waaseelan
Wamina allayli faosjud lahu wasabbihhu laylan taweelan
Inna haola-i yuhibboona al’ajilata wayatharoona waraahum yawman thaqeelan
Nahnu khalaqnahum washadadna asrahum wa-itha shi/na baddalna amthalahum tabdeelan
Inna hathihi tathkiratun faman shaa ittakhatha ila rabbihi sabeelan
Wama tashaoona illa an yashaa Allahu inna Allaha kana ‘aleeman hakeeman
Yudkhilu man yashao fee rahmatihi waalththalimeena a’adda lahum ‘athaban aleeman